18#include "DMDataBlock.h"

22#include <vector>

24namespace ZXing {
25namespace DataMatrix {
26
27std::vector<DataBlock> DataBlock::GetDataBlocks(const ByteArray& rawCodewords, const Version& version)
28{
29 // First count the total number of data blocks
30 // Now establish DataBlocks of the appropriate size and number of data codewords
31 auto& ecBlocks = version.ecBlocks();
32 std::vector<DataBlock> result(ecBlocks.numBlocks());
33 int numResultBlocks = 0;
34 for (auto& ecBlock : ecBlocks.blockArray()) {
35 for (int i = 0; i < ecBlock.count; i++) {
36 auto& item = result[numResultBlocks++];
37 item._numDataCodewords = ecBlock.dataCodewords;
38 item._codewords.resize(ecBlocks.codewordsPerBlock + ecBlock.dataCodewords);
39 }
40 }
41
42 // All blocks have the same amount of data, except that the last n
43 // (where n may be 0) have 1 less byte. Figure out where these start.
44 // TODO(bbrown): There is only one case where there is a difference for Data Matrix for size 144
45 int longerBlocksTotalCodewords = Size(result[0]._codewords);
46 //int shorterBlocksTotalCodewords = longerBlocksTotalCodewords - 1;
47
48 int longerBlocksNumDataCodewords = longerBlocksTotalCodewords - ecBlocks.codewordsPerBlock;
49 int shorterBlocksNumDataCodewords = longerBlocksNumDataCodewords - 1;
50 // The last elements of result may be 1 element shorter for 144 matrix
51 // first fill out as many elements as all of them have minus 1
52 int rawCodewordsOffset = 0;
53 for (int i = 0; i < shorterBlocksNumDataCodewords; i++) {
54 for (int j = 0; j < numResultBlocks; j++) {
55 result[j]._codewords[i] = rawCodewords[rawCodewordsOffset++];
56 }
57 }
58
59 // Fill out the last data block in the longer ones
60 bool specialVersion = version.versionNumber() == 24;
61 int numLongerBlocks = specialVersion ? 8 : numResultBlocks;
62 for (int j = 0; j < numLongerBlocks; j++) {
63 result[j]._codewords[longerBlocksNumDataCodewords - 1] = rawCodewords[rawCodewordsOffset++];
64 }
65
66 // Now add in error correction blocks
67 int max = Size(result[0]._codewords);
68 for (int i = longerBlocksNumDataCodewords; i < max; i++) {
69 for (int j = 0; j < numResultBlocks; j++) {
70 int jOffset = specialVersion ? (j + 8) % numResultBlocks : j;
71 int iOffset = specialVersion && jOffset > 7 ? i - 1 : i;
72 result[jOffset]._codewords[iOffset] = rawCodewords[rawCodewordsOffset++];
73 }
74 }
75
76 if (rawCodewordsOffset != Size(rawCodewords))
77 return {};
78
79 return result;
80}
81
82} // DataMatrix
83} // ZXing
